            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". It’s not a fun situation, even if everything is covered by your insurance policy. As an enthusiast, one of my worst fears is someone will swipe my beloved vehicle which I have s",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
